- Compile-time API hashing / IAT obfuscation
- Runtime dynamic API resolution (dynamic linking)
- Indirect syscalls (hook evasion)
- DLL unhooking (fresh mapping / “Perun’s fart” technique)
- ETW patching (telemetry suppression)
- APC-based and callback-based execution (EnumPageFilesW, local/remote APC)

Use Cases:
