- Evaluating EDR user-mode hooking resilience against indirect syscalls and unhooking
- Comparing execution techniques (APC vs callback execution) for stability/detection
- Generating Artifact Kit-compatible droppers for controlled red team operations
- Researching defensive detections for ETW tampering, PPID spoofing, and loader behaviors

